data.description: Welcome to your ideal one-level living retreat with a perfect blend of convenience and tranquility! This charming residence is nestled on a spacious 2-acre lot, offering the best of both worlds – the serenity of proximity to Sherburne Wildlife Refuge and the accessibility of being close to parks, schools, and the town of Becker. As you approach the property, a grand and accommodating driveway welcomes you, providing ample space for multiple vehicles. The property boasts not one, but two garages, offering an abundance of storage space and possibilities for hobbyists or car enthusiasts. One of the standout features of this home is the expansive mudroom, a practical and well-organized space designed to accommodate the storage of outdoor gear, footwear, and more. Don't miss the chance to make it your new home!
